Now, every day feels like a fry-day to our lucky readers! You heard it yolks, Alzu and the Middelburg Observer are giving away ten trays of 60 large eggs each week in the egg-citing lucky draw. That is a total of 600 eggs weekly, and an astounding 2 400 eggs in total! The Alzu Egg Competition was launched this week and will be running for the next four weeks. All you have to do to enter is: Buy your weekly copy of the Middelburg Observer and fill out the competition entry form. Drop your entry form off at the Middelburg Observer’s reception, where our competition box is available. Make sure you submit your week’s entries by 16:00 on a Tuesday. Readers are welcome to enter as many times as they wish! The more you enter, the greater your chance of winning.